OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FYvette Cooper has rejected calls
OL,8,Fbacked by Harriet Harman for a ban on
OL,9,Fdisappearing messages for politicians,
OL,10,Farguing some ministers use the feature
OL,11,Fto protect international relations.
OL,13,FThe foreign secretary said "lots of
OL,14,Fpeople", including herself, had
OL,15,FWhatsApp's auto-delete tool turned on
OL,16,Ffor some exchanges.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
