PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FIt comes amid a row over the emergence
OL,8,Fof exchanges between Lord Peter
OL,9,FMandelson and Chief Secretary to the
OL,10,FPrime Minister Darren Jones which were
OL,11,Fabsent from a tranche of documents
OL,12,Frelating to his appointment as US
OL,13,Fambassador.
OL,15,FThe documents were released by
OL,16,Fgovernment after requests for
OL,17,Ftransparency, after Mandelson as
OL,18,Fsacked from his Washington job over
OL,19,Fhis links to paedophile financier
OL,20,FJeffrey Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FJones, who reportedly told the
OL,8,Fdisgraced peer he was "so sorry" on
OL,9,Fthe day he was sacked, has said he was
OL,10,Famong those who may have lost access
OL,11,Fto some material by not backing up
OL,12,Fwhen switching devices or turning on
OL,13,Fdisappearing messages.
OL,15,FThe revelations have prompted calls
OL,16,Ffor a ban on ministers using the
OL,17,Ffeature, but the foreign secretary did
OL,18,Fnot support this idea when asked.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
