OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,F"I think lots of people use
OL,8,Fdisappearing for some things ` I'm no
OL,9,Fexception, I don't think anybody else
OL,10,Fis either," she said.
OL,12,F"I have seen some foreign ministers
OL,13,Fwho use disappearing messages for all
OL,14,Ftheir communications, in order to
OL,15,Fprevent international relations being
OL,16,Fpassed on separately.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
