CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,F"But no ` I think there's clear
OL,8,Fguidance that we need to follow to
OL,9,Fmake sure that all decisions are
OL,10,Fproperly recorded and anything that
OL,11,Fneeds to be properly recorded is."
OL,13,FHowever, Harman the former deputy
OL,14,FLabour leader, who Prime Minister Sir
OL,15,FKeir Starer recently appointed as an
OL,16,Fadviser on women and girls, said on
OL,17,FThursday that the use of the feature
OL,18,Fmade her "suspicious".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
