OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FSuggesting it should be banned for
OL,8,Fpoliticians, she said: "Why would you
OL,9,Fdisappear the message unless you have
OL,10,Fsomething to hide?"
OL,12,FDowning Street has suggested the prime
OL,13,Fminister retains confidence in his
OL,14,Fchief secretary despite the fallout
OL,15,Fover messages, published in The
OL,16,FSpectator magazine.
OL,18,FJones is said to have written: "You've
OL,19,Fbeen doing such a great job, and you
OL,20,Fworked wonders with Trump. I'm so
OL,21,Fsorry about today."
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@SO]zD@`OU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
