OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FHe also appeared to criticise
OL,8,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, Commons
OL,9,FChief Whip Jonathan Reynolds and
OL,10,Fprominent Labour MP Angela Rayner, who
OL,11,Fwere all Cabinet colleagues at the
OL,12,Ftime, in another message after Lord
OL,13,FMandelson said growth plans were in
OL,14,Ftheir hands.
OL,16,F"It doesn't fill you with confidence,"
OL,17,Fhe reportedly replied.
OL,19,FStarmer and Reeves are among others in
OL,20,Fgovernment who have confirmed they use
OL,21,Fdisappearing messages on WhatsApp.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
