OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FAsked by reporters on a visit to
OL,8,FYorkshire why Jones' messages were not
OL,9,Fincluded in more than 1,000 pages of
OL,10,Fthe so-called Mandelson files released
OL,11,Fby the government on Monday, the prime
OL,12,Fminister did not answer directly.
OL,14,F"We went through a process, it was a
OL,15,Ftransparency process, and the point of
OL,16,Fthat really was to put everything
OL,17,Fbefore Parliament, and people can then
OL,18,Fsee the material and make their minds
OL,19,Fup," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
