OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780689960
OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FThe files have been redacted in a
OL,8,Fnumber of ways, including where the
OL,9,FInternational and Security Committee
OL,10,F(ISC) agreed the information would be
OL,11,Fprejudicial to national security or
OL,12,Finternational relations.
OL,14,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch has said she
OL,15,Fdoes not use disappearing messages on
OL,16,Fher work phone, but revealed on
OL,17,FThursday she does use them on her
OL,18,Fpersonal devices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
