OL,3,CYvette Cooper rejects calls for
OL,4,Cdisappearing messages ban for
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FShe told reporters: "For personal
OL,8,Fphones, I do use disappearing messages
OL,9,Fbecause I get a lot of spam and junk.
OL,10,FAs much as I enjoy the Instagram links
OL,11,Fand TikToks that people try to send
OL,12,Fme, it does clog up my phone."
